About us
Jack's Seafood Bar and Grill is a fun, casual restaurant where you can find the freshest seafood at reasonable prices. For the seafood lovers, we have oysters on the half shell, crab cakes, steamed shrimp, and fresh fish delivered daily. For the ‘landlubbers’, there are wings, soups, salads, pasta, chicken and burgers also available.
We offer live entertainment 7 nights a week showcasing local bands playing classic rock to alternative, to current rock hits. We also host a blues & brews series every year and have weekly karaoke, trivia night and bingo!
sports enthusiasts can catch their games on 45 televisions and 2 projectors throughout the restaurant with satellite packages for football, baseball, basketball and hockey. Our full menu is available for carry-out including specials. To place an order, call ahead at
239-594-3460
.
